---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import FormContact from "./forms/FormContact.astro";
---

<section id="contact" class="px-4 md:my-16 my-4">
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-current mb-2">Contacto</h2>
        <p class="">
            ¡Gracias por tu interés en mi trabajo! Si tienes alguna propuesta,
            duda o simplemente quieres saludar, puedes encontrarme y escribirme
            directamente a través de cualquiera de estos medios.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <a
                    href="https://linkedin.com/in/tu-usuario"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[currentColor] md:hover:bg-zinc-900 duration-300 group"
                >
                    <Icon
                        name="simple-icons:linkedin"
                        class="h-6 w-6 text-[currentColor] md:group-hover:text-[#0077B5] transition-colors"
                    />
                    <span
                        class="font-medium md:group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >LinkedIn</span
                    >
                </a>

                <a
                    href="https://github.com/tu-usuario"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[currentColor] md:hover:bg-zinc-900 duration-300 group"
                >
                    <Icon
                        name="simple-icons:github"
                        class="h-6 w-6 text-[currentColor] md:group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                    />
                    <span
                        class="font-medium md:group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >GitHub</span
                    >
                </a>

                <a
                    href="mailto:tu-correo@email.com"
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[currentColor] md:hover:bg-zinc-900 duration-300 group"
                >
                    <Icon
                        name="lucide:mail"
                        class="h-6 w-6 text-[currentColor] md:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
                    />
                    <span
                        class="font-medium md:group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >Mail</span
                    >
                </a>

                <a
                    href="https://wa.me/tu-numero-aqui"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[currentColor] md:hover:bg-zinc-900 duration-300 group"
                >
                    <Icon
                        name="simple-icons:whatsapp"
                        class="h-6 w-6 text-[currentColor] md:group-hover:text-[#25D366] transition-colors"
                    />
                    <span
                        class="font-medium md:group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >WhatsApp</span
                    >
                </a>

                <a
                    href="https://goo.gl/maps/tu-enlace-de-google-maps"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-[currentColor] md:hover:bg-zinc-900 duration-300 group sm:col-span-2"
                >
                    <Icon
                        name="lucide:map-pin"
                        class="h-6 w-6 text-[currentColor] md:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors"
                    />
                    <span
                        class="font-medium md:group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >Comunidad Valenciana, España</span
                    >
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <FormContact />
    </div>
</section>
